        "content": "<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Cardinal.mk_int#doc\">docs#Cardinal.mk_int</a></li>\n<li>basically <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/549f950ffa3478a7c5c62c31b940ed4b01ef268d/Mathlib/Data/Real/Cardinality.lean#L202-L205\">https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/549f950ffa3478a7c5c62c31b940ed4b01ef268d/Mathlib/Data/Real/Cardinality.lean#L202-L205</a></li>\n<li><code>example (Œ± Œ≤ Œ≥ : Type*) : Cardinal.mk (Œ± √ó Œ≤ ‚Üí Œ≥) = Cardinal.mk (Œ± ‚Üí Œ≤ ‚Üí Œ≥) := Cardinal.mk_congr (Equiv.curry Œ± Œ≤ Œ≥)</code></li>\n</ul>",
